HEADWORD: Ketmie
<hw>Ket`mie"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The name of certain African species of <gen>Hibiscus</gen>,
cultivated for the acid of their mucilage.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>ketmia</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
